@$OpenBSD$
Map \*[Lq]\*[Rq] to \[lq]\[rq] for all terminal devices (merged upstream).
--- tmac/doc-nroff.orig	Tue Nov  4 09:38:35 2014
+++ tmac/doc-nroff	Fri Apr 14 21:04:21 2017
